policy.title: Privacy & Policies
policy.subtitle: Your trust is important to us. Please review our policies to understand how we protect your information and serve you better.

content.subtitle: Information We Collect
content.text: We collect information that you provide directly to us, including your name, email address, phone number, and appointment details when you book our services or create an account.

content.subtitle: How We Use Your Information
content.text: We use the information we collect to provide, maintain, and improve our services, to process your bookings, to communicate with you about appointments and promotions, and to enhance your experience with RENFAYE LASHES.

content.subtitle: Data Security
content.text: We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

content.subtitle: Your Rights
content.text: You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. Please contact us if you wish to exercise these rights.

content.subtitle: Booking Confirmation
content.text: All appointments must be confirmed via phone, email, or through our online booking system. You will receive a confirmation message once your booking is complete.

content.subtitle: Cancellation Policy
content.text: We require at least 24 hours notice for cancellations or rescheduling. Cancellations made with less than 24 hours notice may be subject to a cancellation fee of 50% of the service cost.

content.subtitle: Late Arrivals
content.text: Please arrive on time for your appointment. If you arrive more than 15 minutes late, we may need to reschedule your appointment or reduce service time to accommodate other clients.

content.subtitle: No-Show Policy
content.text: Failure to show up for a scheduled appointment without prior notice will result in a no-show fee equivalent to 100% of the service cost.

content.subtitle: Service Satisfaction
content.text: Your satisfaction is our priority. If you are not completely satisfied with your service, please contact us within 48 hours, and we will work to make it right.

content.subtitle: Product Returns
content.text: Unopened products may be returned within 14 days of purchase for a full refund. Products must be in their original packaging and unused. Opened products cannot be returned due to hygiene reasons.

content.subtitle: Refund Processing
content.text: Approved refunds will be processed within 5-7 business days to the original payment method.

content.subtitle: Service Corrections
content.text: If you experience any issues with your lash extensions within 48 hours of application, we offer complimentary touch-ups or corrections.

content.subtitle: Hygiene Standards
content.text: We maintain the highest hygiene standards. All tools are sanitized between clients, and we use disposable items wherever possible.

content.subtitle: Allergies & Sensitivities
content.text: Please inform us of any allergies or sensitivities before your appointment. We offer patch tests for clients with sensitive skin or concerns about allergic reactions.

content.subtitle: Health Conditions
content.text: Certain health conditions may affect your ability to receive lash extension services. Please disclose any eye infections, conditions, or recent eye surgeries.

content.subtitle: Aftercare Requirements
content.text: Proper aftercare is essential for the longevity of your lash extensions. We provide detailed aftercare instructions that must be followed to maintain your lashes and prevent complications.

content.subtitle: Service Agreement
content.text: By booking and using our services, you agree to follow our policies and procedures. We reserve the right to refuse service to anyone who does not comply with our policies.

content.subtitle: Liability
content.text: While we take every precaution to ensure your safety and satisfaction, RENFAYE LASHES is not liable for any allergic reactions, sensitivities, or complications that may arise despite proper disclosure and patch testing.

content.subtitle: Changes to Policies
content.text: We reserve the right to update these policies at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page and will take effect immediately upon posting.
